{"type":"message","id":"738c4379","parentId":"a8fd6e44","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:06:06.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到配置里 Moonshot API Key 已经配置了，但 web_search 返回 401 认证错误。这可能是因为 API Key 无效或者过期了。不过我注意到我们已经有 OpenClaw 的官方仓库信息，而且基于现有的项目文档，我可以整理出一篇关于 OpenClaw 最新开发进展的文章。\n\n让我先创建 wechat_articles 目录并开始撰写文章：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dsrodf52ugvov7bx3iaf6d3u","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":3094,"output":143,"cacheRead":21816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774829149036}}
