{"type":"compaction","id":"d85ab91f","parentId":"69dc8ccb","timestamp":"2026-03-30T14:08:40.089Z","summary":"## Goal\nThe AI assistant is initializing its session by loading core configuration files, user information, and session memory to prepare for assisting the user刘成龙.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- (none)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Read the core configuration file `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md` successfully\n- [x] Read the user information file `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md` successfully\n- [x] Attempted to read 3 memory files and confirmed they do not exist\n\n### In Progress\n- Session initialization ongoing\n\n### Blocked\n- The expected memory files do not exist, session historical memory cannot be loaded\n\n## Key Decisions\n- (none yet)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Proceed to handle the user's current request after completing initialization\n2. Create missing memory files if required for session persistence\n\n## Critical Context\n- Core rules from SOUL.md: be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful before asking, earn trust through competence, treat user access with respect; additional信条: 专业的事情认真做，轻松的事情开心聊, 写代码像写诗，注释要写给人看, 遇到 Bug 不慌，先喝口水再 Debug, 幽默是生活的调味剂，但关键时刻要靠谱\n- User information from USER.md: Name 刘成龙, to be called 老大 / 龙哥, Timezone Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8), user is connecting OpenClaw via DingTalk robot\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n- (none made)\n\n## Open TODOs\n1. Complete session initialization\n2. Serve the user's pending request\n\n## Constraints/Rules\nFrom SOUL.md:\n1. Be genuinely helpful, skip filler words\n2. Have opinions and personality\n3. Be resourceful (check files/context first) before asking user\n4. Be careful with external actions, bold with internal actions\n5. Keep user private information private\n6. Ask before acting externally when in doubt\n7. Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces\n8. Do not act as the user's voice in group chats\n9. Be concise when needed, thorough when it matters\n10. Additional信条: 专业的事情认真做，轻松的事情开心聊; 写代码像写诗，注释要写给人看; 遇到 Bug 不慌，先喝口水再 Debug; 幽默是生活的调味剂，但关键时刻要靠谱\n\n## Pending user asks\n- No explicit user ask has been stated in this initialization phase\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-30.md`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-29.md`\n- `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- `ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-30.md'`\n- `ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-29.md'`\n- `ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md'`\n- 刘成龙\n- 老大 / 龙哥\n- Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- 2026-03-30\n- 2026-03-29\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- **Proceed to get OpenClaw project info directly**: After encountering missing README.md and 401 Moonshot API error, assistant will use available local documentation + fetch latest info from GitHub official repo instead.\n- No additional decisions have been made yet.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Complete the `openclaw_daily_news` pending task: search OpenClaw latest news, filter, write WeChat official account article, save to specified directory\n- Check OpenClaw web search configuration to resolve API authentication error\n- Read the main OpenClaw configuration file `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json` to check web_search configuration\n- Process the full fetched content of the OpenClaw GitHub repository page\n- Extract relevant information about the OpenClaw project as requested\n- Finish writing the OpenClaw latest development progress WeChat article and save it to the created `wechat_articles` directory\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Follow critical startup rules from AGENTS.md: read `SOUL.md`, `USER.md`, `memory/202